    @Namespace(value="H5")
@NoOffset
public static class hdf5.DataType
extends hdf5.H5Object
    \class DataType \brief Class DataType provides generic operations on HDF5 datatypes.

    DataType inherits from H5Object because a named datatype is an HDF5 object and is a base class of ArrayType, AtomType, CompType, EnumType, and VarLenType.
